{"type":"message","id":"09bb1858","parentId":"bda86938","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:19:04.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nGut, ich habe die README. Jetzt muss ich die einzelnen Skills genauer anschauen, um eine fundierte Analyse zu liefern. Lass mich die SKILL.md Dateien der einzelnen Skills fetchen, um zu verstehen was sie genau bieten. Parallel schaue ich mir auch das bestehende Setup an.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n\nLass mich die einzelnen Skill-Details und das bestehende Setup genauer anschauen."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_YRTAFhurljs80jsUyNlOHK4J","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":10000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/obsidian-markdown/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_akVw0cyLzU9HZsqSuy2ZwEwX","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":10000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/obsidian-bases/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_y0Td0lvhcTZyXRcCweGoKh4n","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":10000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/obsidian-cli/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_oaUNOLQeeT39gpIjJHxWRFVE","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":10000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/json-canvas/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_r12GSybp7PKtwQMn6rk6UNAV","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":10000,"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kepano/obsidian-skills/main/skills/defuddle/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_end3h2ibZv24ZdcYggrvWede","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\Andrew Openclaw\\Kimi_Agent_ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Implementiert\" -Recurse -Depth 2 -Name 2>$null | Select-Object -First 80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":130,"output